李景亮于2016年5月18日因反兴奋剂药检未通过（盐酸[[克伦特罗|克伦特罗]]呈阳性），8月23日被[[内华达州运动员委员会|内华达州运动员委员会]]禁赛<ref>{{cite web |title=又是瘦肉精惹的祸？UFC中国选手李景亮药检未过 |url=http://sports.ifeng.com/a/20160824/49832589_0.shtml |website=凤凰体育 |accessdate=2018-11-28 |archive-date=2018-11-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181128211037/http://sports.ifeng.com/a/20160824/49832589_0.shtml |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |author1=Marc Raimondi |title=Li Jingliang tests positive for clenbuterol, temporarily suspended by NAC, but not USADA |url=https://www.mmafighting.com/2016/8/23/12615934/li-jingliang-tests-positive-for-clenbuterol-temporarily-suspended-by |website=MMA Fighting |accessdate=2018-11-28 |archive-date=2018-11-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181128211006/https://www.mmafighting.com/2016/8/23/12615934/li-jingliang-tests-positive-for-clenbuterol-temporarily-suspended-by |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2016年8月26日就关于此事件发表声明，解释其原因为[[瘦肉精|瘦肉精]]所导致<ref>{{cite web |title=UFC中国选手李景亮对瘦肉精事件发布声明 |url=http://www.sohu.com/a/113334186_440343 |website=搜狐体育 |accessdate=2018-11-28 |archive-date=2018-11-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181128210755/http://www.sohu.com/a/113334186_440343 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2016年9月2日[[美国反兴奋剂协会|美国反兴奋剂协会]]发布声明表示由于李景亮体内被查出的盐酸克伦特罗含量很低，决定不对李景亮进行任何处罚<ref>{{cite web |title=美国反兴奋剂协会单方面决定不处罚李景亮 |url=http://sports.ifeng.com/a/20160911/49952681_0.shtml |website=凤凰体育 |accessdate=2018-11-28 |archive-date=2018-11-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181128210957/http://sports.ifeng.com/a/20160911/49952681_0.shtml |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |author1=Marc Raimondi |title=USADA won’t sanction UFC’s Li Jingliang in clenbuterol case |url=https://www.mmafighting.com/2016/9/2/12774236/usada-won-t-sanction-ufc-s-li-jingliang-in-clenbuterol-case |website=MMA Fighting |access-date=2018-11-28 |archive-date=2018-11-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181129012708/https://www.mmafighting.com/2016/9/2/12774236/usada-won-t-sanction-ufc-s-li-jingliang-in-clenbuterol-case |dead-url=no }}</ref>。9月13日，内华达州运动员委员会取消对李景亮的禁赛，并宣布将不对他进行任何处罚<ref>{{cite web |title=“吸血魔”李景亮免于处罚，将在UFC206出战查得 莱普里斯 |url=http://sports.ifeng.com/a/20161016/50108514_0.shtml |website=凤凰体育 |accessdate=2018-11-28 |archive-date=2018-11-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181128212419/http://sports.ifeng.com/a/20161016/50108514_0.shtml |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |author1=Marc Raimondi |title=Li Jingliang clear of doping suspension from NAC, slated to fight Chad Laprise at UFC 206 |url=https://www.mmafighting.com/2016/10/14/13290768/li-jingliang-off-doping-suspension-from-nac-slated-to-fight-chad |website=MMA Fighting |accessdate=2018-11-28 |archive-date=2018-11-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181128210843/https://www.mmafighting.com/2016/10/14/13290768/li-jingliang-off-doping-suspension-from-nac-slated-to-fight-chad |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

=== 插眼事件 ===
2018年2月11日，李景亮在UFC221对战杰克·马修斯的比赛中，一次插眼行为引起争议<ref>{{cite web |title=Jake Matthews cops savage eye gouge from Li Jingliang at UFC 221 |url=https://www.sportingnews.com/au/mma/news/jake-matthews-eye-gouge-ufc-221-lin-jingliang-perth/1mb4shd68dpzl1990puwd4xrr3 |website=Sport news |accessdate=2018-11-28 |archive-date=2018-11-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181128210956/https://www.sportingnews.com/au/mma/news/jake-matthews-eye-gouge-ufc-221-lin-jingliang-perth/1mb4shd68dpzl1990puwd4xrr3 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。其所在的拳天下俱乐部给出回应称：针对比赛中有所争议的“扣眼睛”动作，景亮当时的位置无法看到对手的脸在哪里，在缠斗中用力挣脱，并不存在故意犯规。杰克·马修斯也也在其社交网站上发表声明：“请忘记插眼的事关注这场比赛本身，我很尊敬李景亮”<ref>{{cite web |title=关于李景亮“插眼”，国外拳迷是这么评价的！ |url=http://www.sohu.com/a/222780636_589989 |website=搜狐体育 |accessdate=2018-11-28 |archive-date=2019-04-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190427235254/http://www.sohu.com/a/222780636_589989 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

